Welcome to libfabbri's documentation!
=====================================

This library implements analytical calculations for :math:`\mathbf{B}` -- the
magnetic field, :math:`\mathbf{W}` -- the scalar potential, and
:math:`\mathbf{V}` -- the vector potential for uniformly and linearly
magnetised tetrahedra based on Massimo Fabbri's 2008 and 2009 papers
:cite:p:`fabbri:2008, fabbri:2009`. The library used for
multiprecision calculations is :ref:`MPFR C++ <http://www.holoborodko.com/pavel/mpfr/>` :cite:p:`holoborodko:2010` which makes
use of MPFR :cite:p:`fousse-et-al:2007`. For unit testing we use the Catch2
library :cite:p:`catch2:2017`. 

